         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Chief Secretary's Office ¶ Melbourne ¶ ,  ¶ 22nd Augt  ¶ 18 ¶ 96. ¶  ¶ Baron Von Mueller called to day to ask me to undertake, in the event of his decease, to see through the press the next edition of...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">96.08.22</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">Charles Topp to Alexander Peacock</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">C96/6948, unit 894, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; font-style: italic; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See G. Luehmann to C. Topp, 14 October 1896.</p>
               </note>Chief Secretary's Office</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Melbourne</seg>
               <seg>, </seg>22nd Augt <seg style="font-style: italic; ">18</seg>96.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Baron Von Mueller called to day to ask me to undertake, in the event of his decease, to see through the press the next edition of the Census of Australian Plants, he has added 1080 manuscript additions to the printed lists and another edition should be published next year or the year after[.]<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> I promised to undertake this work</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">C A. T</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Register and p. a</p>
         </div>
      </body>
